      <title>乌克兰巩固哈尔科夫防线，俄罗斯推进查西夫亚尔附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/russia-advances-near-chasiv-yar-as-ukraine-bolsters-kharkiv-line</link>
